CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: GD Culture Group Ltd, formerly Code Chain New Continent Ltd, is a holding company. The Company is engaged in the business on research, development and application of Internet of Things (IoT). The Company also engaged in the business on research, development and application of electronic tokens Wuge digital door signs. The wuge digital door signs combine the five-W elements (when, where, who, why, what), geographic location via the Beidou satellite system and identity information using Code Chain technology.
